Build scripts for cross-compiling OpenOCD on Windows via mingw32 on Linux

NOTE: Currently only Debian is supported.

INSTRUCTIONS:

1. Download/extract scripts
2. run build.sh to start the build

build.sh willi:
- install any missing packages that are requied (e.g. gcc-mingw32)
- download and cross-compile libusb-win32-src-1.2.5.0
- download and cross-compile libftdi-0.19
- 'git clone' openocd repository and cross-compile w/ libftdi support
